# Mermaid Test File (.mmd)

This is a test file with `.mmd` extension to verify the extension works with both file types.

## Sequence Diagram
```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Alice
    participant B as Bob
    A->>B: Hello Bob!
    B-->>A: Hello Alice!
    A->>B: How are you?
    B-->>A: I'm good, thanks!
```

## Flowchart
```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start --> Decision{Is it working?}
    Decision -->|Yes| Success[Great!]
    Decision -->|No| Debug[Debug issue]
    Debug --> Fix[Apply fix]
    Fix --> Decision
    Success --> End[Done]
```

